To build Bomb-her-man :
./autogen.sh
make
sudo make install

By default, it will be installed into /usr/local.
If you want it to be installed into /usr, just pass --prefix=/usr to autogen.sh

Player 1 : use the arrows to move, right shift to plant bomb
Player 2 : use esdf to move, space to plant bomb

The AI doesn't do anything for now
